{"tid":249450,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚連登潛水撚同冰球撚(ice hockey)","createTime":"2017-05-19T10:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T13:22:11.000Z","uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"784a54b6dbc2170be9a4c3e2e34aa7bcb0d24536","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:06:31.000Z","msg":"求問各位巴絲打<br />\n想學潛水,叫做識小小自游式,但唔識踩水,外加唔敢係水入面除泳鏡開眼,但就自問唔係好怕水既,咁可唔可以去學潛水呢?(scuba)<br />\n之前追post連登好似係有dive instructor,如果有巴絲係既可唔可以報個價黎聽下?毒撚一個,如果有其他巴絲有興趣都可以join埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ntg:HkgMorningStar<br />\n另外都想問埋連登有無巴絲有打開ice hockey?呢個都有興趣想玩,不過唔知點入門/入行,有打開既可唔可以點條路我行下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ce50f86e89e117fe7b51df2948d49d934f2747","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"十連無難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397bc43f2a8d3b7c4b5e51319369f0af1ca1678d","tid":249450,"uid":12782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"啱啱學<br />\n唔識水底反壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762e0ddde483d2571596f408ac3cc6cf677916d4","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱學<br />\n唔識水底反壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前係台灣試體驗潛水個陣我發現向耳仔谷氣呢個方法對自己唔係好work,反而係吞口水work(唔知你係咪講緊呢樣野),當然可能係我捉唔到個技巧啦,不過你都可以試下唔同方法"},{"pid":"6c48f7459a64c879d3c0a03b20ddbb144d57b780","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱學<br />\n唔識水底反壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前係台灣試體驗潛水個陣我發現向耳仔谷氣呢個方法對自己唔係好work,反而係吞口水work(唔知你係咪講緊呢樣野),當然可能係我捉唔到個技巧啦,不過你都可以試下唔同方法</blockquote><br />\n再次挑戰十連<br />\n1"},{"pid":"933ecbc2adcfbfe656eb1435d1218036f00d08d3","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T11:59:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啱啱學<br />\n唔識水底反壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前係台灣試體驗潛水個陣我發現向耳仔谷氣呢個方法對自己唔係好work,反而係吞口水work(唔知你係咪講緊呢樣野),當然可能係我捉唔到個技巧啦,不過你都可以試下唔同方法</blockquote><br />\n再次挑戰十連<br />\n1</blockquote><br />\n2"},{"pid":"d8296ae076b87b4a9d079e668e03a365c290b9ee","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啱啱學<br />\n唔識水底反壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前係台灣試體驗潛水個陣我發現向耳仔谷氣呢個方法對自己唔係好work,反而係吞口水work(唔知你係咪講緊呢樣野),當然可能係我捉唔到個技巧啦,不過你都可以試下唔同方法</blockquote><br />\n再次挑戰十連<br />\n1</blockquote><br />\n2</blockquote><br />\n3"},{"pid":"d7e6edb784186deba8ef659151d277c9c972d49d","tid":249450,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"潛水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識朋友唔識潛水都照玩"},{"pid":"ad1bbabca0c9b4aef32967454e27a8f1f94b21a6","tid":249450,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"香港學大部份都差唔多價，你打潛水課程好多"},{"pid":"7de6df27d12272d3291bbf75cf6dca445ff8fa93","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>潛水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識朋友唔識潛水都照玩</blockquote><br />\n你指唔識游水?無水試咩?間間都寫要水試既"},{"pid":"a5d1d134fdae1094f754e1a6a7314ada72d41009","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港學大部份都差唔多價，你打潛水課程好多</blockquote><br />\n諗住有巴打PM個下順便問下小小野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1150218c422ca31055f39ecf01f973193f5c418e","tid":249450,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"Rescue diver<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但仲係50潛無gear既廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc115fd194a6938986e05af6c716bd943243a6b7","tid":249450,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>潛水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識朋友唔識潛水都照玩</blockquote><br />\n你指唔識游水?無水試咩?間間都寫要水試既</blockquote><br />\n外國學唔洗水試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n潛過就知唔識游/游水極廢都潛到水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fedb52e1b68384b60a0d8aab9a31fad977adeb","tid":249450,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:43:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱學<br />\n唔識水底反壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前係台灣試體驗潛水個陣我發現向耳仔谷氣呢個方法對自己唔係好work,反而係吞口水work(唔知你係咪講緊呢樣野),當然可能係我捉唔到個技巧啦,不過你都可以試下唔同方法</blockquote><br />\n有時係水底唔係好吞到口水<br />\n正常都係鏈住鼻 鼻大力噴氣谷到耳仔度"},{"pid":"9ecc1efcdae65bb60f22211a38d63bef9c1351a2","tid":249450,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>潛水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識朋友唔識潛水都照玩</blockquote><br />\n你指唔識游水?無水試咩?間間都寫要水試既</blockquote><br />\n香港大潛水店好似主要都係PADI<br />\n我有朋友唔識游水既<br />\n<br />\n冇可能唔洗水試既,你點都叫考緊個潛水牌你學完唔落水做番佢教既野佢點簽比你呢.所以筆試同水試都有,<br />\n另外聽講有教練會要求學生踏下水 游番幾廿米咁囉<br />\n<br />\n(要考好快D考,呢家水都重叫清,過多排就好差,直到中秋先會清)"},{"pid":"e8dbc5da99fa23dbfbb9169fb6838b100b690229","tid":249450,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱學<br />\n唔識水底反壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前係台灣試體驗潛水個陣我發現向耳仔谷氣呢個方法對自己唔係好work,反而係吞口水work(唔知你係咪講緊呢樣野),當然可能係我捉唔到個技巧啦,不過你都可以試下唔同方法</blockquote><br />\n反到就得,唔洗介意用咩方法"},{"pid":"dd4d11c4c56943ed732ef1b5357b7ccfaf7eeb42","tid":249450,"uid":4207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"DM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊考埋教練"},{"pid":"e9f3328f467c3b8b2a47396f0588b0a9246f541e","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>潛水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識朋友唔識潛水都照玩</blockquote><br />\n你指唔識游水?無水試咩?間間都寫要水試既</blockquote><br />\n香港大潛水店好似主要都係PADI<br />\n我有朋友唔識游水既<br />\n<br />\n冇可能唔洗水試既,你點都叫考緊個潛水牌你學完唔落水做番佢教既野佢點簽比你呢.所以筆試同水試都有,<br />\n另外聽講有教練會要求學生踏下水 游番幾廿米咁囉<br />\n<br />\n(要考好快D考,呢家水都重叫清,過多排就好差,直到中秋先會清)</blockquote><br />\n就係水試呢樣野比較麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 游水都超級十分之差...踩水就更加唔使諗tim...所以都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22490924b75d87eda91c9f4410a69551de947a3","tid":249450,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>潛水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識朋友唔識潛水都照玩</blockquote><br />\n你指唔識游水?無水試咩?間間都寫要水試既</blockquote><br />\n香港大潛水店好似主要都係PADI<br />\n我有朋友唔識游水既<br />\n<br />\n冇可能唔洗水試既,你點都叫考緊個潛水牌你學完唔落水做番佢教既野佢點簽比你呢.所以筆試同水試都有,<br />\n另外聽講有教練會要求學生踏下水 游番幾廿米咁囉<br />\n<br />\n(要考好快D考,呢家水都重叫清,過多排就好差,直到中秋先會清)</blockquote><br />\n就係水試呢樣野比較麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 游水都超級十分之差...踩水就更加唔使諗tim...所以都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去東南亞學囉"},{"pid":"78314fdadded258222d8da724ec7a0a03b80aa43","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>潛水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識朋友唔識潛水都照玩</blockquote><br />\n你指唔識游水?無水試咩?間間都寫要水試既</blockquote><br />\n香港大潛水店好似主要都係PADI<br />\n我有朋友唔識游水既<br />\n<br />\n冇可能唔洗水試既,你點都叫考緊個潛水牌你學完唔落水做番佢教既野佢點簽比你呢.所以筆試同水試都有,<br />\n另外聽講有教練會要求學生踏下水 游番幾廿米咁囉<br />\n<br />\n(要考好快D考,呢家水都重叫清,過多排就好差,直到中秋先會清)</blockquote><br />\n就係水試呢樣野比較麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 游水都超級十分之差...踩水就更加唔使諗tim...所以都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去東南亞學囉</blockquote><br />\n第一無錢,第二無假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係香港學完出到去全程享受仲好啦"},{"pid":"f0fc59f6db6f19aadb547a30b6d70cc570e693da","tid":249450,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>潛水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識朋友唔識潛水都照玩</blockquote><br />\n你指唔識游水?無水試咩?間間都寫要水試既</blockquote><br />\n香港大潛水店好似主要都係PADI<br />\n我有朋友唔識游水既<br />\n<br />\n冇可能唔洗水試既,你點都叫考緊個潛水牌你學完唔落水做番佢教既野佢點簽比你呢.所以筆試同水試都有,<br />\n另外聽講有教練會要求學生踏下水 游番幾廿米咁囉<br />\n<br />\n(要考好快D考,呢家水都重叫清,過多排就好差,直到中秋先會清)</blockquote><br />\n就係水試呢樣野比較麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 游水都超級十分之差...踩水就更加唔使諗tim...所以都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去東南亞學囉</blockquote><br />\n第一無錢,第二無假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係香港學完出到去全程享受仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n學潛水三日就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你預前後再多一日 5日就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d5a64c188b94931f4a8231390e6a39e5e51859","tid":249450,"uid":83606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"經驗分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常係耳仔開始覺得有小小feel就要反壓<br />\n如果痛先反就遲左，通常會唔work<br />\n所以當你feel到有野壓住又未到痛就好反壓<br />\n咁就可以完美反壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb515433861489b37b7ff7246ea6dbc79eabcc94","tid":249450,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>潛水撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識朋友唔識潛水都照玩</blockquote><br />\n你指唔識游水?無水試咩?間間都寫要水試既</blockquote><br />\n香港大潛水店好似主要都係PADI<br />\n我有朋友唔識游水既<br />\n<br />\n冇可能唔洗水試既,你點都叫考緊個潛水牌你學完唔落水做番佢教既野佢點簽比你呢.所以筆試同水試都有,<br />\n另外聽講有教練會要求學生踏下水 游番幾廿米咁囉<br />\n<br />\n(要考好快D考,呢家水都重叫清,過多排就好差,直到中秋先會清)</blockquote><br />\n就係水試呢樣野比較麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 游水都超級十分之差...踩水就更加唔使諗tim...所以都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去東南亞學囉</blockquote><br />\n第一無錢,第二無假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係香港學完出到去全程享受仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n學潛水三日就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你預前後再多一日 5日就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n身為一個勞工,你幾時產生左你可以有假放既錯覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f485a55e1cb47b420ead33f41ec450c2382c093","tid":249450,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:37:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br